reviewText:
It's Just Ok to me. Not to the level of my Expectation. Shockingly Enough, it happens to be the same as the "C.B in Concert, Rock & Roll Music" with the Sole Difference of the Pictures on the Cover. Since I had just Received that One, So I felt bad that I had just gotten a Double of it.
Needless, but don't have the time to return it, so Will Simply Give it to a Friend!
